headline: The Schwab Mortgage-Backed Securities ETF (SMBS) Starts Trading
summary: WESTLAKE, Texas, November 19, 2024--Schwab Asset Management®, the asset management arm of The Charles Schwab Corporation, announced the Schwab Mortgage-Backed Securities ETF (NYSE Arca: SMBS) began trading today.
